					<font isBold="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[3. Tax on Interest Payments]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="27" y="460" width="163" height="30" uuid="952c94b3-3747-4e24-9723-ba1a4a18543c"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Left" verticalAlignment="Middle">
					<font isBold="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[4. Principal Recovery]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="27" y="490" width="500" height="40" uuid="0d5c7d33-a7c6-48ad-a319-404ceed76514"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html"/>
				<text><![CDATA[The principal amount will be the difference between the EMI and the interest amount calculated for the month. Repayment Allocation to Principal will be done as per the Allocation Order specified in Para 5 below.]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="27" y="530" width="163" height="30" uuid="0b7d99bc-b82e-4b96-b1ea-188b6d42484d"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Left" verticalAlignment="Middle">
					<font isBold="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[5. Allocation of Repayments]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="27" y="560" width="500" height="190" uuid="ffd13373-5c42-4694-a857-83f64af8ddd7"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html"/>
				<text><![CDATA[Without prejudice to the Loan Agreement, any payment made by the Borrower/s to the Company under the Loan Agreement shall be appropriated by the Company in the following order.<br><br>
1. Cheque/ECS/NACH Bounce Charges<br>
2. Additional Interest<br>
3. Any other charges incurred by the Company on behalf of the Borrower/s under the Loan<br>
4. Interest portion of EMI<br>
5. Principal portion of EMI<br>
6. Partial / Full Pre-payment and connected Charges, if any<br><br>
The Company reserves the right to refuse acceptance of post-dated cheques or such other instrument towards payments or settlement of credit facility. The company has rights to present the cheque/ECS/NACH multiple times for collecting overdue payment as and when borrower becomes delinquent.]]></text>
